Thank you for registering with Skirball for this coming semester.

<% if @purchase.courses.present? %>
    Our records show you are registered for the following course(s):

    <% @purchase.courses.each do |course| %>
        "<%= course.title %>" on <%= course.day_of_week %>, <%= course.start_time %> - <%= course.end_time %> beginning <%= course.class_dates.first.start_time.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>.

        The course will take place at <%= course.location.address %>.

    <% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @purchase.events.present? %>
    Our records show you are registered for the following event(s):

    <% @purchase.events.each do |event| %>
        "<%= event.title %>" on <%= event.date.strftime('%m/%d/%Y') %> starting at <%= event.time %>

        This event will take place at <%= event.location.address %>.

    <% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @purchase.total > 0 %>
    Your total for this purchase is <%= number_to_currency @purchase.total %>, which will be charged to your credit card.

<% end %>
You registered with the following contact information:

<%= "#{@purchase.first_name} #{@purchase.last_name}" %>
<%= @purchase.account.email %>
<%= @purchase.address %>
<% if @purchase.address2.present? %>
    <%= @purchase.address2 %>
    <%= "#{@purchase.city}, #{@purchase.state} #{@purchase.zip}" %>
<% else %>
    <%= "#{@purchase.city}, #{@purchase.state} #{@purchase.zip}" %>
<% end %>

